==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Invariant
<hw>In*va"ri*ant</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Math.)</fld>
<def>An invariable quantity; specifically, a function of the
coefficients of one or more forms, which remains unaltered, when these
undergo suitable linear transformations.</def> <rj><au>J. J.
Sylvester.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Invasion</ent>⟦br⟧
